<exercise id="fs-idm133171248">
<problem id="fs-idm132367664">
<para id="fs-idm155279760">From which component of the light-dependent reactions does NADPH form most directly?</para>
<list id="fs-idp32033184" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>photosystem II</item>
